{"tid":1944102,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"法國地道式Hea游滑雪","createTime":"2020-03-26T07:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T07:06:37.000Z","uid":14095,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1cc29641b9eeffaf170f02f0260ec074f08272","tid":1944102,"uid":14095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"今次去得8日 主要見一見d朋友同滑雪 <br />\n係2月既事 個時歐洲仲未爆 再遲反幾日真係GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見冇咩做就出個POST 初體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過HEA多 冇咩點影相 有D係IG CAP番出黎算 都係當紀錄下<br />\n同埋我又鍾意體驗LOCAL生活 有法國仔帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下點生活既可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外反正好多人知我連登AC 不用相認THX<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391a138f763d0ed059efbcf008bb3d76a561e71d","tid":1944102,"uid":14095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfnLXXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfnLXXe.jpg&h=0f76f69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDnoKK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDnoKK3.jpg&h=6c7af52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁夜晚12點機 要轉機 LONDON -&gt; BCN , 之後再渣車入法南<br />\n上機前係Lounge飲左好多黑啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2EuFa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2EuFa0.png&h=5871200a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFmdnpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFmdnpP.png&h=d5a668bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英航D STAFF係咁問我飲唔飲啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又飲左幾觀就訓左 倫敦LHR冇咩好講就skip<br />\n咁到左之後我FD渣車黎接機 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvE20bg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvE20bg.jpg&h=437372af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tOVLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tOVLb.png&h=c914a4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztsW4Ey.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FztsW4Ey.png&h=2e65b618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便講下 因為佢住既地方城市叫Perpignan <br />\n算係法國同西班牙交界 渣車去BCN機埸就2H30M,算近 <br />\n咁岩我又想睇下聖家堂 同埋西班牙妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁機埸出區好快 30M左右 咁就睇左聖家堂<br />\n真係好撚震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇過既最震撼就係真理聖殿同埋呢個聖家堂 2個都係未起好 係呢2個睇完先比到個O撚左既感覺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻扯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxAtVOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxAtVOe.png&h=24b700f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9yn0e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9yn0e1.png&h=9b6ad975&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8ybTz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8ybTz9.png&h=01d09346&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqPB4GW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqPB4GW.png&h=7217225e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrRkMVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrRkMVp.png&h=51078aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wvBEh2m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvBEh2m.png&h=4fce8362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngRkMVO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngRkMVO.png&h=25e10b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hP0xC2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhP0xC2B.png&h=d0170e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpg1wnK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frpg1wnK.png&h=d83bbc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GXpFMWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGXpFMWa.png&h=245f5739&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"613a45494857d984f13bf947de59c8f9a3488e4a","tid":1944102,"uid":14095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"利伸反黎已自我隔離14日加機場全程K94<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef784586e474cba568b3f09397a3fa6e1ab00843","tid":1944102,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"留個名 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14748389d8a019b0e1ab5d69aeb7cafdc3e1fa9f","tid":1944102,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf92f36f8dc9778ee5d4749b74bfad84eef416a0","tid":1944102,"uid":14095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Od4Zigv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOd4Zigv.png&h=03b59c12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfKnf3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfKnf3g.jpg&h=139414f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後食TEA 就比佢發板,火腿好正 芝士好正 飲酒好CHILL <br />\n見到D西班牙妹好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地話同法國妹唔同 早熟好多 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPt3KWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPt3KWU.png&h=cb105f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去埋米拉之家望望<br />\n就番機埸去接另一個FD 之後就開始坐車番入法國<br />\n超市買左d野食 煮左餐招呼下咁<br />\n番到去都9點幾<br />\n<br />\n (咁佢間屋係我之後影番既)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6Wg4Zp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6Wg4Zp.png&h=83aa8531&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6srQpZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6srQpZA.png&h=f94a3202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個肥仔佢老豆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1e4ynMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1e4ynMr.png&h=91e0573a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j537sdf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj537sdf.png&h=040c4a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NX0Ndq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NX0Ndq.png&h=b3261a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2LYyTz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2LYyTz.png&h=ebcc6c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個棟野係佢其中一個房黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢有3棟係後面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMwAA7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMwAA7B.png&h=d4d4890d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後會係呢個位同全個家族既人聚餐<br />\n婆婆大哥兄弟姊妹齊哂係到 之後會講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxGXPsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxGXPsM.png&h=1afe49cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQEqYmg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQEqYmg.png&h=d00d49ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7tGwGq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7tGwGq.png&h=b749bc29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢自己間房有一個套房 廚房 洗手間 客廳先等於佢間房 <br />\n我諗都有500呎<br />\n不過冇影到相 得片 所以唔放上黎啦<br />\n花園我睇最小都有一個足球埸咁 <br />\n其實成個house影相影唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有田種下提子種下檸檬咁 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pogdnOL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpogdnOL.jpg&h=9aa2477c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjUnf9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjUnf9p.jpg&h=e9e51d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一晚就係佢屋企CHILL下咁 開左幾支紅酒飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個trip都飲左10幾支 全部自己野或者d珍藏(佢話)<br />\n睇落都唔平同幾珍貴 詳情就唔知了<br />\n<br />\n話晒好耐冇見 除左屋主呢個朋友 大家都係第到飛過黎 <br />\n不過得我係亞洲出發 最遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以第一晚就都講下近況9UP下咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dddabc8e3c16ae446463d4d4b434d472b7e144","tid":1944102,"uid":14095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"仲講左我好多 類似<br />\n&rdquo;不得不看！10件只有法國人才會做的事情！&rdquo;<br />\n呢d特別野我知 我話反d旅遊撚樣達人話某d野點點點<br />\n佢哋一句bull shit我就Collect skin了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(了解後大概係個情況就好似某d撚樣話香港手信一定係買曲奇咁🤫)<br />\n<br />\n不過都有解釋反 會點做點做<br />\n<br />\n有時間既話會再講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1acd4de9f348eb8e5b48fa48e3f929c9d6ebe79","tid":1944102,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"Ching原來BC撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cl