:14095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"之後第二日就6點起身去左滑雪 <br />\n地方係Andorra <br />\n西班牙同法國之間既一個滑雪好出名的一個小國<br />\n本來想去埋Les trois vall&eacute;es 但果邊我有2個朋友係瑞士個邊 <br />\n<br />\n佢地請唔到假去唔到搞到行程變更<br />\n就去足ANDORRA 4日,渣車去都係2H30M<br />\n咁都係滑下咁 滑陣飲酒 再滑 再飲<br />\n<br />\n呢邊D埸好大 係日本滑左幾年都識睇滑雪埸地圖 但法國D路線係要轉黎轉去先去到 好煩 又唔識法文 還好有FD係到 咁4日好快過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5Eq5B8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5Eq5B8.jpg&h=f86c6c46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMC4BJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMC4BJO.jpg&h=a75c117c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsrw1aP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqsrw1aP.png&h=de1a2983&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDrH7QV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDrH7QV.png&h=aaa95d92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nO0mDXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnO0mDXH.png&h=de525226&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRaBsQ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRaBsQ9.png&h=b9f856d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tB7HopB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtB7HopB.png&h=b1fcdae1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dh8O3pJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdh8O3pJ.png&h=750d3cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fc6XWKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffc6XWKU.jpg&h=b138941b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehqUYYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehqUYYM.jpg&h=965e6dc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ebcbce7ac49b9b58ab3b85f8ca80f58f612daff","tid":1944102,